{"tid":1274223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考評局：許多人錯誤將把法治等同執行法例","createTime":"2019-07-01T15:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:21:03.000Z","uid":266837,"like":1143,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b8ba9483b58ab77a8a9b56e73c3c30cff78478","tid":1274223,"uid":266837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:57:11.000Z","msg":"考評局明日將發表2014年文憑試考試報告，報告中稱，許多人錯誤地理解法治，把法治等同於執行法例。<br />\n<br />\n在通識科試卷中，有題目問及考生，政府管治出現甚麼困難，又問及近年的遊行及檢控數字，反映社會甚麼核心價值出現矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n報告中分析，指考生回答關於政府管治能力的必答題上，表現一般，未能正確地指出政府面對的困難；又指出學生對於言論、示威自由及法治等概念掌握較為薄弱，亦有相當多的人，錯誤認為法治等同於執行法例，部分考生亦只是把法治的意思詮釋為遵守法律，須擴闊及加強認識法治的和功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20141105/s00001/1415190562146/%E8%80%83%E8%A9%95%E5%B1%80-%E8%A8%B1%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%8A%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141105%2Fs00001%2F1415190562146%2F%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258A%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%258B&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNovcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=76c21ce3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141105%2Fs00001%2F1415190562146%2F%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258A%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%258B&h=eff8f372\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20141105/s00001/1415190562146/%E8%80%83%E8%A9%95%E5%B1%80-%E8%A8%B1%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%8A%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B</a>"},{"pid":"19ecf4b4cb5daa0d03d44f8ecd863b1b3931ba9a","tid":1274223,"uid":266837,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"dfec22dbd11e5a24fb3e143afff56b75bedd6004","tid":1274223,"uid":266837,"like":6,"dislike":78,"score":-72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"我掛了p牌 sosad"},{"pid":"92d5ad3641f68d10f11b8e04e427c5bff27b747c","tid":1274223,"uid":179409,"like":497,"dislike":1,"score":496,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"咪話學生<br />\n大部份香港成年人都係咁樣誤解法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782f5a5330a6a23c984e70dbf2b1d6857d1b14bf","tid":1274223,"uid":56453,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa92de149f8ffe3a4229553fff67667b47eecc42","tid":1274223,"uid":2994,"like":186,"dislike":0,"score":186,"quote":{"pid":"92d5ad3641f68d10f11b8e04e427c5bff27b747c","tid":1274223,"uid":179409,"like":497,"dislike":1,"score":496,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"咪話學生<br />\n大部份香港成年人都係咁樣誤解法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"最簡單 好多傻9連俾法官判完先叫有罪都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f43d191d6004ba0e3740999adaa9daef13b430","tid":1274223,"uid":266837,"like":267,"dislike":3,"score":264,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"法治，是與人治相反之概念。與法制不同，法治指以民意授權為前提和基礎立法，以嚴格依法管治國家為核心，以制約權力為關鍵的社會管理機制、社會活動方式和社會秩序狀態。法治的內涵，不單是要求所有人民守法，更側重於法律對政府權力的控制和拘束。<br />\n<br />\n法治意味着每個人都受到法律的約束，包括立法者、行政官員和法官。在這個意義上，法治與統治者凌駕於法律之上的獨裁、人治相對立。<br />\n<br />\n抄:維基"},{"pid":"7208b1583b171c98a80335766c1aa9e3ed99f92b","tid":1274223,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7739a014c3c0634a03c14800890b8b46b88a66","tid":1274223,"uid":259302,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"比建制派誤導"},{"pid":"b1f52ebc4bc6e5a99d5b9b1040e7e2164f2e8831","tid":1274223,"uid":85455,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"92d5ad3641f68d10f11b8e04e427c5bff27b747c","tid":1274223,"uid":179409,"like":497,"dislike":1,"score":496,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"咪話學生<br />\n大部份香港成年人都係咁樣誤解法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"所以咪有好多族群係度「支持政府依法施政、支持警察依法辦事」<br />\n根本法治想達到既係彰顯公義、保持市民既權利、平等&hellip;"},{"pid":"9a248c2bf09b03ad119e56fe14130c6f2f0fb7ef","tid":1274223,"uid":51129,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"以後見到d廢老話後生讀屎片就po返呢段出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f98616bb0135834c29d103d7c967234afa402d9","tid":1274223,"uid":259812,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"咪話學生市民 分分鐘濕鳩高官都唔識"},{"pid":"f5f5fcaaf545c5855f6072c9dda08ca835629d4d","tid":1274223,"uid":179409,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"fa92de149f8ffe3a4229553fff67667b47eecc42","tid":1274223,"uid":2994,"like":186,"dislike":0,"score":186,"quote":{"pid":"92d5ad3641f68d10f11b8e04e427c5bff27b747c","tid":1274223,"uid":179409,"like":497,"dislike":1,"score":496,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:0